Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡休息  基本已經平靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還說已經開始練習走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在心情也平復了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉都這麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  直呼你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不是太親暱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  優
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹嘛  都說了早上要開會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  要抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  可以跑過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我的  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小幡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得不錯嘛  小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了  真透你當夏季大賽的準正式隊員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始的合宿裡我會好好鍛鍊你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好吃苦頭的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  沒想到和小鳥遊能親密到一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好肉麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小幡學姐在合宿時把你這性格改過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃苦頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長的一對一訓練的機會是可遇不可求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  小幡學姐挺嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要聽見那「啾啾」的腳步聲就開始緊張…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是在告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡學姐臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內八字  內八字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶幾條毛巾好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦汗的時候  打翻東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  軟膏軟膏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒做夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥在淚水的藍色中飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繽紛小鳥在繽紛的天空中飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次飛越不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上就會染上不同的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的彩虹色的小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而小鳥想看更多的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色慢慢相互交融  漸漸渾濁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子眼瞳的顏色會變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實沒什麼要緊的事  不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺啊  這個不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿準備成怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩  剛剛優又發簡訊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我「全部收拾好了嗎」還附上了行李清單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透和小優關係真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該算是孽緣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幼稚園到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優雖然現在裝得很正經
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前還是個很奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺總是靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的時候經常在上課時跑出教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  在你正忙的時候打電話過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關係啦  我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再給你發簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被星光的群山擁抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  真透  嘔吐袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理經人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認人的記性不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐一下會舒服很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小幡  你要讓她當準正式隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像不太願意跟其他人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎  反正有理經人在  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有理經人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還沒使出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都會遇上不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不認識的人特別多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那個孩子又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前沙耶老師說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人替你承受各種痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真透的痛就是那孩子來承受的  這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在承受我的痛楚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很帥氣  但是聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  之前偶爾出現的人今天也在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來給我們看看其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  之後再給
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個送給沙耶老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是這個比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這樣暖一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部就走光了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  小幡  那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為日本男兒總希望他能強大一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡那個要買給男生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給他呀  3班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP  STOP  不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那個是給之前那個男生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點可愛呢  小幡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透也想要男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  還太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少等升到高中再說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為真透有小鳥遊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗看  試吃的時候覺得很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  合宿開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優睡覺磨牙太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點睡不著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優咬牙的聲音呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是伴著奇怪的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼在意的事就要說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是最要好的朋友嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  我也送給真透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  顏色不同的  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚了那麼多人在這裡有什麼有趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人婆居然還寫情書呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說合宿帶回來的特產居然是木刀誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  拓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這樣小幡太可憐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確這不符合我的性格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要掛牆頭展示的話我可要收錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩居然笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事根本不是能笑出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她卻笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭的時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今一起度過的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後將要一起度過的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今流下的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後將要流下的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個都一樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了  要來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不該去做不習慣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同學  明明哭出來也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過的話哭出來也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過事情都已經發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強真是讓人心痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑小幡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽  在嘲笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嘲笑小幡同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同學…大家的笑料小幡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強  硬來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同學的心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時小幡同學存在本身也好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝點咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你給絆倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微扭了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  現在可是夏季大賽臨近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真透  來扶我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀…就算有什麼難過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都不想怪罪到別人頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要是怪罪別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就代表自己什麼都沒努力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得原因都在自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就會覺得自己什麼都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何時候都能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何時候都能飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑我的治療肯定不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找保健室的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老師不在的話就找沙耶老師好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶老師就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  都算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點回去練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是偷懶就剝奪你準正式隊員的名額哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點去吧
